{
  "stem": "16571.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 183.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm not even counting the fact that I was having to do what I did, as I was explaining before, about fighting for a few potato peelings, and for maybe some stale bread somebody chucked from a window or whatever.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then, as I said, the story was we eventually got a little bit stronger, those who managed-- in my case, as I was saying to you before, in my case, I was preferring to eat a potato or a lump of hard bread, rather than, say, tins of whatever they were giving you and all the rest of it.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that is-- maybe, it wasn't time for me to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Maybe the Lord up there didn't want me-- it wasn't my time to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's how I survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it wasn't-- Eventually, as the rumors went round, every day-- was about-- must have been sometimes-- August.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Oh, by the way, forget-- I forgot to tell this story.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Was-- It was about August time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Five of us went out for a walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We finished up at this suite of fruit trees.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We filled our pockets up with apples, plums, and a German come out and he shouted, get off my land, or some to that effect.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And one of my friends put his hand in his pocket, and with his finger, he pointed, get out, leave, get away from here or you'll get shot.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Whilst all this was going on, we were laughing and picking this fruit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now, I'm talking about, now, two and a half, three and a half months after liberation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before you could say, good morning, two Jeeps with British Tommies surrounded us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was about-- as I said, there was four, or five, or six of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
